Dear Zoiper customer,

The Zoiper team released a new version of Zoiper5.

You can download the newest release versions from here:

Zoiper5 5.6.11 for Windows 64bit
https://shop.zoiper.com/download.php?id=5FNZ2NTRNZ8JAO8    


Zoiper5 5.6.11 for macOS arm64
