Zoiper5 5.6.11 for Linux 64bit - RPM
https://shop.zoiper.com/download.php?id=TZVL14X9CGJDFZA        
Zoiper5 5.6.11 for Linux 64bit - deb
https://shop.zoiper.com/download.php?id=A7PGTVVBRUBSUV6        
Zoiper5 5.6.11 for Linux 64bit - TAR
https://shop.zoiper.com/download.php?id=53RH8SW3J90PSXN            


To keep you updated with the newest additions and fixes, we bring you the following change-log:

Added "Early Media" call state to Call Event Rules.
Improvement: the crash report window will no longer appear when the Crash Dump option is disabled.
Disabled "Enable Sending Of Typing Notification" by default.

Please follow the steps below to successfully update to the latest version:
1. Click on the link above. If it does not open, please copy and paste it in your browser.
2. You will get the latest Zoiper version for download. Download and install it.
3. Start your new Zoiper. It will ask you for your username and password. Please use your existing username and password. If you do not have them - please use our password recovery https://www.zoiper.com/en/password_recovery.

To get a new download link, manage and reset your licenses or password, please use our login section at https://www.zoiper.com/en/login .

Wishing you a pleasant Zoiper experience!
The Zoiper Team
